axr=ax.ravel()
def ts(fa):
  ts_fa = train_item[train_item.family==fa]
  ts_fa['date']=pd.to_datetime(ts_fa['date']) 
  ts_fa.set_index('date', inplace=True)
  ts_fa = ts_fa.drop(['family'], axis=1)
  return ts_fa 
for i in range(len(l)):
  ts_fa=ts(l[i])
  axr[i].plot(ts_fa.tot_sales)
  axr[i].set_title(l[i])

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

def add_city_map(name,typ):
    folium.Marker(
         location=list(map(add,store_locations.get(name),[(0.5-rd.random())/20,(0.5-rd.random())/20])),
         icon=folium.Icon(color=col.get(typ), icon='shopping-cart'),
    ).add_to(map_Ecuador)
